37
00:02:47.337 --> 00:02:50.090
Belum lagi nikotin dan shiraz.

38
00:02:51.091 --> 00:02:52.050
Kau paham maksudku.

39
00:02:55.679 --> 00:02:57.848
- Aku harus bilang sesuatu.
