59
00:04:07.542 --> 00:04:09.127
pria dan memanggilnya teman.

60
00:04:12.255 --> 00:04:13.298
Wow.

61
00:04:38.573 --> 00:04:42.035
Bagi Mimi, Thomas seperti New York baru.

62
00:04:43.078 --> 00:04:45.372
Tanpa bahaya, tanpa kebebasan.

63
00:04:46.248 --> 00:04:49.793
