69
00:05:38.216 --> 00:05:39.217
Thomas Webb.

70
00:05:41.219 --> 00:05:43.597
- Mengapa pusing, Thomas?
- Apa?


71
00:05:44.556 --> 00:05:46.516
Aku mengenali warna stres.

